verbose_text: Baseline demographics and clinical data recorded included age at FP counseling, BMI (kg/m 2), serum anti-Mullerian hormone (AMH) levels (ng/mL), total antral follicular counts (AFC), type of BC (estrogen receptor (ER), positive or negative), previous parity, partnership status, if the woman has chosen to proceed with FP or not, the reason for not proceeding with FP and the method elected for FP.
